/*----------------------------------------*/
    Multi-Threaded TCP Application
/*----------------------------------------*/

Multi-threaded TCP Server and Client. Server can handle 20 outstanding connections. To demonstrate communication, client prompts for a set of user inputs to send to server.

make clean all --> directs output to release/
make release -> directs output to release/
make debug -> directs output to debug/

Run the following commands from the debug/ or release/ folders
sudo ./tcp_server
sudo ./tcp_client
